author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Well, its been a hell of a ride these past seven years, but Cobra Kai has finally come to an end. Join me and a hand-picked team of Sensei's as we examine the highs and lows of the show, and talk about that epic finale.

title: Happy Hour - Cobra Kai: The Final Season
